  N4 -->|Primary| N5[PB: Process Builder - Implement PO process improvements]
  N5 --> N6[PB: Cortex Monitoring - Monitor and review improvements]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced COGS through improved PO accuracy, faster lead times, and automated process improvements across procurement.]
  N4 -->|High supplier OTD risk detected| B1[Prioritize alternative suppliers]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Improved supplier reliability]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N4 -->|Significant PO accuracy issues identi...| B2[Adjust procurement rules]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Reduced PO errors]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N4 -->|Limited lead time reduction potential| B3[Focus on digitalization opportunities]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Enhanced PO process efficiency]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]